snippet.title: Red Dead Redemption - Outlaws to the End Co-Op Mission Pack Trailer
snippet.description:
This new trailer showcases a brief preview of each of the six missions featured in the free Outlaws to the End Co-Op Mission Pack. Now available for download from PlayStation Network and Xbox LIVE.

www.rockstargames.com/reddeadredemption
 
ESRB Rating: MATURE with Blood, Intense Violence, Nudity, Strong Language, Strong Sexual Content, Use of Drugs
